comments.body:
@copilot please make sure there is a sample image in the demo app that can demonstrate this new feature. Maybe some drop down / picker on the lottie page that allows picking between the base64, the file system and in future, the .lotrie file format. 

In fact, maybe we need to consider the .lottie file format. Please research that and make sure that works. We will have to extract for now, but in future we could use a zip file resource provider or something.

Please make sure this new lottie file format is supported, everything is tested with 90% code coverage and that the sample has all of this demonstrations
